==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Toponym
<hw>Top"o*nym</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A name
of a place.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a name, as in the binomial name of a plant, based
on, or derived from, a place name, or based on the location of the thing
named.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Toponymy</ent>⟦br⟧
